                java.lang.String userAgent,
                java.lang.String destinationDirectory)

        Value type that represents a Download.

        Parameters:
        url - The full url to the content that should be downloaded.
        fileName - A canonical filename for this download.
        contentType - Content type (MIME type) to indicate the media type of the download.
        contentLength - The file size reported by the server.
        userAgent - The user agent to be used for the download.
        destinationDirectory - The matching destination directory for this type of download.
